U.S. FTC Says Oil Price Fixing Action Hinges on ’Wrongdoing’

-- B y   J e f f   B l i s s
-- 
2011-05-17T18:13:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-17/ftc-says-oil-price-fixing-action-hinges-on-wrongdoing-1-.html
The U.S. Federal Trade Commission,
responding to a request from five Democratic senators, said it
will “take action whenever we find wrongdoing” involving the
fixing of gasoline prices.  To contact the reporter on this story:
